## 2026-05-29 20:00 WIB — Section 1: Adversarial audit + hardening + LOCK

- **fix(atomicity)**: `internal/brain/write.go::AddDrawerFull` wrap drawer+FTS insert dalam `db.BeginTx` (sebelumnya: 2 separate Exec — kalau FTS gagal setelah drawer commit, drawer ada tapi tidak searchable → silent inconsistency).
- **fix(dos/memory)**: `handlers_brain_ingest.go` apply `http.MaxBytesReader(w, r.Body, 16MB)` di submit + batch (sebelumnya: caller bisa POST 100MB body → OOM, cap batch jalan SETELAH parse).
- **fix(dos/cpu)**: `internal/ingest/sanitize.go::Sanitize` cap input ke `MaxSanitizeBytes = 256KB` di awal (sebelumnya: loop ReplaceAll O(n²) untuk input pathological whitespace).
- **lock**: 4 file Section 1 di-mark LOCKED — `internal/ingest/{ingest,sanitize,score}.go` + `handlers_brain_ingest.go`. Section 2 (Re-score worker), Section 4 (compounding worker), Section 5 (embedding pipeline) → TAMBAH function/file baru, JANGAN modify locked file tanpa approval Mr.Dev.

### Audit deferred items (tidak fix sekarang — alasan eksplisit):
- **Error message generic prefix** (`fmt.Errorf("insert drawer: %w", err)` bisa expose SQLite column/constraint detail ke HTTP body): single-owner deployment, debug-value > leak-risk. Defer sampai multi-tenant.
- **Embedding generation**: roadmap acknowledge defer ke Section 5 (Embed worker). Saat ini FTS BM25 cukup untuk dedupe + basic retrieval.
- **Doc chunker** (`ChunkIndex` param exists, helper `ChunkDoc(text)` tidak ada): caller harus chunk sendiri lalu batch. Defer sampai ada doc importer real.
- **Backpressure SubmitBatch worker pool**: serial loop OK untuk single writer SQLite. Defer sampai concurrent writer atau distributed.
- **Federation source endpoint** (`source_type='federation'` taxonomy declared, tidak ada dedicated endpoint): caller pakai /submit dengan `source_type:"federation"` cukup. Dedicated endpoint defer ke Section 17 (Knowledge share / mesh).

